Class JsonElement

java.lang.Object
com.github.egyptian_league.json.src.JsonElement
Direct Known Subclasses:
JsonArray, JsonNull, JsonObject, JsonPrimitive
public abstract class JsonElement extends Object
JsonElement is the abstract base class for all Json elements.
